Delta Forms ESOP: Delta Air Lines took steps to place nearly 20% of its stock 
in friendly hands, in what appeared to be a corporate takeover defense. The 
Atlanta-based airline said a newly formed employee stock ownership plan would 
control 14% of its shares and that Swissair, a foreign airline, would acquire 
