<DOCNO> LA071189-0078 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 80712 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 11, 1989, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 2; Column 6; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
23 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bob Carpenter, acquired in a trade last January that sent Steve Kasper to the 
Kings, signed a one-year contract with the Boston Bruins. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
