<TEXT>
<P>
Doug Flutie has signed a one-year contract with the New England Patriots of the 
National Football League that reportedly will pay him at least $350,000 in base 
pay and could be worth more than $1 million. 
</P>
<P>
If Flutie, 26, starts at least eight games this season, his salary would 
increase to about $900,000 and, depending on how much he plays, he could earn 
more than $1 million. 
</P>
