ESTANCIA'S MAKI TOPS JUNIOR GOLF QUALIFYING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Austin Maki of Estancia High School shot rounds of 68-70 for a 138 at Rancho 
Bernardo Golf Club Monday to lead four golfers who qualified for the 1989 U.S. 
Junior Amateur Championship, July 25-29 at Singing Hills Country Club in El 
Cajon. 
</P>
<P>
